\v 10 Khona uzaphahlaza\x + 51.63,64. Isam. 18.21.\x* isiphiso emehlweni amadoda ahamba lawe;\x + 19.10. 1 Kho. 14.3.\x*
\v 11 ubususithi kiwo: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla:\x + 51.63,64. Isam. 18.21.\x* Ngokunjalo ngizabaphahlaza lababantu lalumuzi,\x + 13.14.\x* njeng\add omuntu\add* ephahlaza imbiza yombumbi,\x + Isa. 30.14. Hlab. 2.9. Lilo 4.2.\x* engebuye ilungiswe futhi; njalo baza\add ba\add*ngcwaba eThofethi, ngoba kungasoze kube lendawo yokungcwaba.\x + 7.32.\x*
\v 12 Ngizakwenza njalo kulindawo, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, lakwabakhileyo bayo, ukuthi ngenze lumuzi \add ube\add* njengeThofethi.\x + 2 Kho. 23.10.\x*
\v 13 Njalo izindlu zeJerusalema lezindlu zamakhosi akoJuda zizangcoliswa njengendawo yeThofethi,\x + 2 Kho. 23.10.\x* ngenxa yazo zonke izindlu abatshisela phezu kwempahla zazo impepha\x + 32.29; 44.18,21. 2 Kho. 23.12. Zef. 1.5.\x*\x + 2 Sam. 11.2.\x* kulo lonke ibutho lamazulu,\x + Seb. 7.42. Dute. 4.19.\x* bathululela abanye onkulunkulu iminikelo yokunathwayo.\x + 7.18.\x*
