\v 14 Khona wabuya uJeremiya evela eTofethi,\x + 2 Kho. 23.10.\x* lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayimthume khona ukuprofetha, wasesima egumeni lendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*,\x + 26.1. 2 Lan. 20.5.\x* wathi ebantwini bonke:
